div.div:
Note
P01 codes are more specific then P35 codes.
P35 codes are groupes with several P01 codes.
Not each P01 has a P35 code.
For some P01 codes that we use, we created dummy P35 codes (EXTRA001 - EXTRA007).
Some measurements come from monitoring stations with a fixed location, some come from moving vehicles like ferry boxes.
Measurement records that are left out: unknown location, empty value, redundant measurement.
